data.description: Even When it Is Full, It's Roomy! Come take a look at this spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bath with split floor plan offering everyone privacy. Tile flooring is throughout the home except for the bedrooms which are carpeted. The master suite is spacious offering 2 closets  and a separate shower and soaking tub, along with dual sinks, making the morning rush more bearable. A large open great room is great for gatherings opening up to the under truss screened porch. The utility room offers a washer and dryer as well as a spacious pantry and is situated between the 2 car garage and kitchen. Seller will give a $3,000. credit towards replacement of carpeting. Take a look for yourself, You will be glad you did!
